node.text: Gardens of the Mind Capsule for the Monday Program™. Our signature hoodie, long sleeve and short sleeve tees featuring screenprint and embroidered applications. Releasing tomorrow in-stores and online.
Kith ++ Ksubi. Available now at Kith shops and Kith.com.

We developed two custom plaid flannels for Kith ++ Ksubi which have been washed down to achieve a worn-in soft hand feel. These flannels have been combined with our denim to create the Reversible Denim Jackets, the detachable Hooded Apollo Jackets, the 2-in-1 Kash Parker Vests, and the Kace Zip Shirts. Releasing tomorrow in-stores and online.

We’ve reimagined Ksubi’s staple Chitch and Van Winkle denim through our lens for Spring ‘20. We’ve created four washes of the Chitch and two washes of the Van Winkle, all of which feature hand distressed details and updated co-branding. Releasing tomorrow.
Lookbook for Kith ++ Ksubi. Collection releases this Friday. Full lookbook and info now live on the site.

Campaign for Kith ++ Ksubi. A full men’s and women’s collection that introduces new silhouettes and reimagined staples. Collection releases this Friday at Kith shops and Kith.com. Full campaign and info now live on the site.
Kith ++ Ksubi. Coming soon.
We took a new approach to our Denim Program™ for Spring 2020, as we’ve worked with Ksubi to channel their meticulously crafted denim and fits through our signature lens. Kith ++ Ksubi coming soon.
Kith for the G-Shock Metal GM6900 Rose Gold. Available now at Kith shops and Kith.com
R&D testing in the G-Shock Lab of our Rose Gold GM6900. Water, Shock, vibration, and scratch resistant. G-Shock’s signature toughness with a luxury approach. Releasing tomorrow.

Kith for the G-Shock GM6900 Rose Gold. We are proud to introduce the first metal-faced GM6900 ever, a luxury take on an iconic model. Presented in our own rose gold finish, this watch features a Kith-engraved button, two Kith Monogram™ resin straps in black and white, and custom packaging. Releasing for this upcoming Monday Program™ in-stores and online.

Kith for the G-Shock 6900 25th Anniversary. As told by the creator and founder of G-Shock,
Mr. Kikuo Ibe. Coming soon.

For tomorrow’s Monday Program™ we are celebrating the premiere of Colette’s documentary “Colette, Mon Amour”. We will be hosting a pop-up shop with Colette and Highsnobiety to launch products inspired by the doc on the 2nd floor of our SoHo flagship from 2/6-10. Ahead of the opening, we collaborated with Colette one more time with this hoodie. Releasing tomorrow at Kith shops and Kith.com.
The Ronnie Fieg x New Balance 1700 Colorist™ Capsule is available now in-stores and online
The Colorist™ Capsule by Kith for New Balance. Releasing tomorrow at all Kith shops and at 11AM EST on Kith.com.

Kith x New Balance Williams 3 Hoodies & Paneled L/S Tees. Our signature 500 GSM fleece and heavyweight jersey in two ombré tie-dyed washes with custom Kith & New Balance patches. Releasing this Friday in-stores and online.
Kith x New Balance Colorist Track Suits. Asymmetrically paneled nylon quarter zip jackets and track pants. Releasing this Friday in-stores and online.

Ronnie Fieg for the New Balance Made in USA 1700. 1,700 total pairs between both styles were produced and will only release at Kith shops and Kith.com this Friday. There will be no wider global launch.
Will Mercado for The Colorist™ by @kith @ronniefieg @newbalance. Full release info today.

The Kith Incense Chamber for the Monday Program™. 100% Carrara marble engraved with our logo and signature herringbone pattern. Comes in custom packaging with incense. Releasing this coming Monday at all Kith shops and Kith.com.
The Kith Incense Chamber for the Monday Program™. 100% Carrara marble with engraved detailing. Releasing this Monday.
